data.title: Royal Births Announcements 2011
data.meta_description:
Welcome to the thread for Royal births in 2011.

Please feel free to contribute to this thread.

Please follow the forum rules when posting.

The original...
data.text:
2010 (became kown in 2011):

1 January: Princess Ida of Thurn and Taxis, first child of Prince Alfonso of Thurn and Taxis and his wife Princess Anna, née Countess of Trauttmannsdorf-Weinsberg

An Online Gotha: Thurn and Taxis

10 January: Duke Alexander of Württemberg, first child of Duke Eberhard of Württemberg and his fiancée, Desirée Copf.

(Duke Eberhard and Desirée Copf got married in 2011)

Descendants of King Louis Philippe I of the French (second part)

19 May: Prince Francisco of Auersperg, first child of Prince Andreas of Auersperg and his wife Princess Maria née Serrana Pintos Pizzichillo.

An Online Gotha: Auersperg

10 September: Prince Juan Sebastian of Auersperg, first child of Prince Ferdinand of Auersperg and his wife Princess Mercedes, née Garcia Gebelin.

An Online Gotha: Auersperg

13 September: Archduke Johannes Maria of Austria, first child of Archduke Johannes and Archduchess Gabriela of Austria, née Montenegro.

Eurohistory: * Archduke Johannes Maria of Austria (b. 2010)

8 November: Archduchess Katharina of Austria, third child and first daughter of Archduke Maximilian and Archduchess Maya of Austria, née Askari.

Eurohistory: * Archduchess Katharina of Austria (b. 2010)

7 December: Maria de Orleans e Bragança Ratto, second child and first daughter of Princess Maria Francisca d'Orleans e Braganza and Bernardo Almeida Braga Ratto.

Descendants of King Louis Philippe I of the French

December 2010: Lola Alejandra Garrido, first daughter and second child of Princess Sarah bint Assem of Jordan and Alejandro Garrido.

--------

January:

2 January: Princess Muneerah of Brunei, second child and first daughter of Crown Prince Billah and Princess Sarah of Brunei, née Rahaman. TOPIC

8 January: Prince Vincent and Princess Josephine of Denmark, third and fourth children and second son and second daughter of Crown Prince Frederik and Crown Princess Mary of Denmark, née Donaldson. TOPIC

15 January: Princess Nicolaia of Auersperg-Breunner, third child and third daughter of Prince Johann of Auersperg-Breunner and his wife Princess Maria Phillippa, née Countess Calice.

22 January: Princess Sophia of Thurn and Taxis, second child and second daughter of Prince Alfonso and Princess Anna of Thurn and Taxis, née Countess of Trauttmansdorff-Weinsberg.

30 January: Augustin, son of Prince Anton Clemens von Croy and of an woman whose name is unknown.

February:

2 February: Prince Balthasar of Auersperg-Breunner, second son and second child together of Prince Alexander and Princess Elisabeth of Auersperg-Breunner, née Flick.

12 February: Archduke Luigi of Austria, fourth child and third son of Archduke Martin and Archduchess Katharina of Austria, née Princess of Isenburg.

25 February: Paola ten Cate, second child and second daughter of Princess Margarita de Bourbon de Parma and Tjalling ten Cate.

February: Count Martin of Habsburg, third son and fourth child of Archduke Mattias and of Austria, Prince of Tuscany, and Countess Eva of Habsburg, née Anderle.

March:

1 March: Countess Marie of Stolberg-Wernigerode, third child and first daughter of Prince Georg and Princess Katja of Stolberg-Wernigerode, née von Kienlin.

27 March: Archduchess Amaya Anna of Austria, first child of Archduke Philipp and Archduchess Mayasuni of Austria, née Heath.

March: Elizabeth Long, second child and second daughter of Ragnhild (née Lorentzen) and Aaron Long.

April:

7 April: Princess Blanca of Bourbon-Two Sicilies, sixth child and second daughter of Prince Pedro and Princess Sofia of Bourbon-Two Sicilies, Duke and Duchess of Noto, née Landaluce.

19 April: Comte Léopold of Limburg-Stirum, first child of Comte Rodolphe and Comtesse Marie Christine of Limburg-Stirum, née Archduchess of Austria

May

05 May: Countess Katharina and Countess Johanna of Stolberg-Stolberg, first and second child of Count Nicolas and Countess Susannah of Stolberg-stolberg, née Handtke.

24 May: Prince Amedeo of Savoy-Aosta, second son of Prince Aimone of Savoy-Aosta, Duke of Apulia and his wife Princess Olga, née Princess of Greece. TOPIC

30 May: Alvaro Gomez Acebo, third child and third son of Bruno en Barbaro Gomez Acebo, née Cano y de la Plaza.

June:

8 June: Eudes and Valentina de Orléans e Bragança, first and second child and first son and first daughter of Don Eudes en Dona Patricia de Orléans e Bragança, née Landau.

10 June: Béatrice and Raphaëlle de Quelen, second and third child and second and third daughter of Count Olivier and Countess Hedwig de Quelen, née Princess of Liechtenstein.

15 June: Prince Alfred of Auersperg, first child of Prince Alexander and Princess Emma of Auersperg, née Feilden.

21 June: Sheikh Hamdan bin Mansour bin Zayed bin Sultan Al Nahyan of Abu Dhabi, third child together and second son together of Sheikh Mansour bin Zayed bin Sultan Al Nahyan of Abu Dhabi and his second wife, née Sheikha Manal bint Mohammed bin Rachid Al Maktoum of Dubai.

July:

10 July: Princess Philomena of Schaumburg-Lippe, second daughter and second child together of Fürst Alexander and Fürstin Nadja of Schaumburg-Lippe, née Zsoeks.

26 July: Princess Iryana Leila Pahlavi of Iran: first daughter and only child of the late Prince Ali Reza Pahlavi of Iran and his fiancée, Ms. Raha Didevar.

29 July: Levon Khanna, first son and first child of Princess Michelle Lobkowicz and Vish Khanna.

July: Prince Richard Ssemakookiro van Uganda, child of Kabaka (= King) Ronald Muwenda Mutebi of Uganda and a woman from the Enseneene (grasshopper) clan. (second son and fifth child of the King)

August:

03 August: Prince Joseph of Caraman-Chimay, first son and second child of Prince Charles Joseph and Princess Amicie Caraman-Chimay, née Countess of Ursel.

03 August: Count Alexander of Toerring-Jettenbach, second child and second son of Count Carl-Theodor and Countes Natalia of Toerring-Jettenbach, née Ivanova.

05 August: Princess Nazira Safya of Perak, first daughter and second child of the Crown Prince and Princess of Perak, Raja Dr Nazrin Shah and Tuanku Zara Salim, née Davidson.

September:

16 September: Princess Frida of Saxony, second daughter of Prince Arne and Princess Sara of Saxony, née Schneider.

22 September: Prince Karl Egon of Fürstenberg, first child of Prince Antonius and Princess Mathilde of Fürstenberg, née Countess Borromeo.

27 September: Prince Giorgi Bagration Bagrationi of Georgia, first son and first child together (3rd for the Princess) of Prince David Bagrationi-Mukhranel of Georgia and Princess Anna Bagrationi-Gruzinsky of Georgia.

27 September: Princess Salome of Oettingen-Oettingen and Oettingen-Wallerstein, second daughter and second child of Prince Friedrich and Princess Isabella of Oettingen-Oettingen and Oettingen-Wallerstein, née Bonelli.

Oktober:

9 October: Princess Lalla .. of Morocco, first daughter and second child of Prince Moulay Ismaël and Lalla Anissa of Morocco, née Lehmkuhl.

17 October: Princess Masamba Nkwanzi of Bunyoro-Kitara, first daughter together and second child together of Omukama (= King) Solomon Gafabusa Iguru and Omugo (=Queen) Margaret Karunga of Bunyoro-Kitara.

21 October: Countess Xenia Coudenhove-Kalergi, first child of Count Dominik and Countess Adélheid Coudenhove-Kalergi, née Princess of Liechtenstein.

October: Maximilian Tessmar-Pfohl, first son and fourth child of Countess Theresa of Stolberg-Stolberg and Alexander Tessmar-Pfohl.

November:

02 November: Sheikha Aisha bint Mohammed bin Hamad Al-Sharqi of Fujairah, first daughter and second child of the Crown Prince of Fujairah, Sheikh Mohammed bin Hamad al-Sharqi, and his wife, née Sheikha Latifa bint Mohammed al-Maktoum of Dubai.

05 November: Princess Fatimah Al-Alia bint Hashem of Jordan, third daughter and third child of Prince Hashem bin Al Hussein and Princess Fahdah Hashem of Jordan, née Mohammed Abu Neyan.

10 November: Countess Charloote Creutz, second child and second daughter of Count Fredrik and Countess Annunziata Creutz, née Princess of Bourbon-Two Sicilies.

December:

10 December: Princess .. Sing of Jodhpur, first child of Crown Prince Shivraj Sing and Princess Gayatri of Jodhpur, née Princess of Askot.

17 December: Maximilian von Lattorf, second son and seventh child of Princess Tatjana of Liechtenstein and Philip of Lattorff.

23 December: Sheikh Zayed bin Sultan bin Hamdan al-Nahyan of Abu Dhabi, child of Sheikh Sultan bin Hamdan al-Nahyan of Abu Dhabi and his wife.

28 December: Princess Giulia of Liechtenstein, third child and second daughter of Prince Alfred Paola and Princess Alice of Liechtenstein, née Stori Deserti.
